===Verb===
'''[[get]] one's [[foot]] [[in]] the [[door]]'''
#{{idiom}} To gain [[attention]]; to [[begin]] to establish a [[reputation]] or accumulate [[experience]], as at a [[job]].
#:''He's overqualified for the position, but he figures he'll do the job for a little while, just to '''get his foot in the door''' at Acme.''